{Pupils, Staff, and Curriculum}
The School is divided into a class of{ {22 Infants}(4-7 years) and a class of{ {16 Juniors}(7-ll years). At 11 Years old the Children go to Newent Comp. There is a Headmistress, an Infant Teacher, 2 part-time teachers, a Welfare Assistant,a Clerical Assistant (who is also meals supervisor) and a cleaner (who is also the lunchtime supervisor)
We use the{Ginn 360 Reading Scheme, and the{Nuffield Maths Scheme.}We use a BBC'B'Computer with disc drive, a colour T.V., a radio, a gramophone, a videotape recorder and audiotape recorders.{Favourite T.V. programmes- "Zig-Zag", "Look and Read" and "My "World".{Favourite radio programmes are "Listen" and "Let's Move"
